      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Mar 30 excerpts from Pres Bush's news conference referring to his reasons for opposing limits on carbon dioxide emissions</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Excerpts from President Bush's news conference yesterday rendered a word incorrectly in some editions in a comment by Mr. Bush on his reason for opposing limits on the emission of carbon dioxide. Referring to an energy crisis, he said, ''And that's why I decided to not have mandatory caps on CO2 .'' He did not say ''to now have mandatory caps on CO2 .''</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
